        "Action description and web link to further information^^": "The Green Tech Fund (GTF) was established in 2020 to provide better and more focused funding support to research and development projects which can help Hong Kong decarbonise and enhance environmental protection. A total of $400 million has been allocated to the GTF. As at July 2025, 33 projects, involving a total grant of about HK$147 million, from local universities, designated public research institutes and private enterprises have been approved.\\n\\nhttps://www.gtf.gov.hk \\n",
