        "Identified financing model": "Public finance- own budget",
        "Project description and URL link, if applicable": "Installations of Renewable Energy in wastewater treatment and stormwater drainage facilities:\\n\\nPhase 1 [Total cost of projects HKD 52M, all completed] The projects involve provision of renewable energy installations in various wastewater treatment and stormwater drainage facilities. The installations include a combined heat and power generating system, micro-turbine generating system and photovoltaic systems. \\n\\nPhase 2 [Total cost of projects HKD 145M, in which HKD 117M of projects were completed] The projects involve provision of renewable energy installations in various wastewater treatment facilities. The installations include facilities for food waste/ sewage sludge co-digestion, hydro-turbine generating system and photovoltaic systems.\\n\\nPhase 3 [Total cost of projects HKD 62M, in which HKD 41M of projects were completed] The projects involve provision of renewable energy installations in various wastewater treatment facilities. The installations include those which harness (i) waste heat of combined heat and power generators, (ii) hydropower arising from sewage flow, and (iii) solar energy.\\n\\nPhase 4 [Total cost of projects HKD 122M, in which HKD 62M of projects were completed] The projects involve provision of renewable energy installations in various wastewater treatment facilities. The installations include facilities for increasing capacity of food waste/ sewage sludge co-digestion, digestion of imported sludge, combined heat and power generating system and photovoltaic systems. \\n\\nPhase 5 [Total cost of projects HKD 5M, all completed] The projects involve provision of pilot floating photovoltaic systems in suitable water bodies.\\n\\nPhase 6 [Total cost of projects HKD 70M, in which HKD 4M of projects were completed] The projects involve provision of renewable energy installations in various wastewater treatment facilities. The installations include combined heat and power generating system, floating photovoltaic systems and ultrasonic sludge pre-treatment system.\\n\\nPhase 7 [Total cost of projects HKD 11M] The projects involve provision of renewable energy installations in various wastewater treatment facilities. The installations include photovoltaic systems.\\n\\nPhase 8 [Total cost of projects HKD 26M] The projects involve provision of renewable energy installations in various wastewater treatment facilities. The installations include combined heat and power generating system, and photovoltaic systems.\\n\\nPlease refer to the link below for further details: https://www.dsd.gov.hk/EN/Sewerage/Environmental_Consideration/Renewable_Energy/\\n",
