        "Describe how the factor supports or challenges the adaptive capacity of your jurisdiction": "New Taipei City maintains a stable political structure and has established strong working relationships with both the national and other municipal governments in addressing climate change, particularly in terms of resource coordination and knowledge sharing. The city plans to allocate an annual climate budget to stimulate private-sector green investment and create green employment opportunities.\\n\\n"
