        "Specify if target is considered a science-based target (SBT) and the SBT methodology it aligns to": "No, our jurisdiction does not consider the target to be science-based (select future intention to set a SBT): Other: OPCC and reference to national policy objectives",
        "Emissions covered by target in most recent inventory (metric tonnes CO2e)": 16890000.0,
