        "If target type is renewable energy: Percentage of total energy that is renewable in target year": 70.0,
        "Is this target publicly available?": "Other: https://ncsd.ndc.gov.tw/Fore/nsdn/about0/2050Path",
        "Progress made towards target": " This target refers to the energy goal proposed by the central government in 2022. As there is no statistical data available for the target year, the renewable energy share of 11.90% as of the end of 2024 is reported in the \\'target year index value\\' field. This figure is based on the 2023 electricity generation statistics provided by the Taiwan Power Company.\\n\\nAs electricity supply in Taiwan is planned and managed by the centrally authorized Taiwan Power Company, which operates power plants nationwide and allocates electricity to all municipalities, the \\'estimated emission reduction of the action year\\' for each action listed under Question 9.2 of this questionnaire has already taken into account the central government's renewable energy targets."
