        "Response": "Yes",
        "Provide an attachment to the strategy addressing emissions from consumption of the most relevant goods and services": "新北市舊衣收集再利用設施設置管理要點 113年修訂.pdf",
        "Provide a link, if applicable, and highlight any specific action the jurisdiction is implementing to reduce emissions from the consumption of goods and services in this category": "https://www.epd.ntpc.gov.tw/Download?catID=1938 \\n\\nThe \\'Key Points for Management of Setting Up Used Clothes Collection and Reuse Facilities in New Taipei City\\' is formulated for the cleaning team's or recycling bins' collection of used clothing and trousers that are still usable for the use of social groups with mental or physical disabilities."
