        "Status of financing": "Other: Funding has been secured",
        "Identified financing model": "Public finance- own budget",
        "Project description and URL link, if applicable": "The Baogao Smart Industrial Park in Xindian is designed to attract production industries that meet the criteria of low or zero pollution, focusing primarily on smart city sectors such as digital health, AI, ICT, and cloud computing, as well as low-pollution manufacturing. Companies from the electric vehicle sector, such as Hon Hai and Tesla, have already moved into the park.\\n\\nThe first phase of the park, with an investment of NT$4.1 billion, was completed in 2022. The buildings obtained both the Gold-level Green Building Label and the Silver-level Intelligent Building Label. The development integrates the concepts of production, living, and ecology, offering a flexible and synergistic industrial space that accommodates R&D, design, testing, and manufacturing needs of the smart city industries. It also features a 5G infrastructure and comprehensive living amenities, forming a new forward-looking park that embodies the idea of “Three Livings in One.” The second phase is scheduled for completion in 2026, with an estimated NT$27 billion in investment.\\n\\nIn the future, the Baogao Smart Industrial Park will serve as a key base for advancing green industries. In addition to factory offices and conference facilities, it will include testing fields, inspection centers, youth innovation incubation centers, and R&D offices. All buildings in the park will target Gold-level Green Building certification, and will be supported by an ecological restoration plan for the surrounding environment. It is estimated that the CO₂ emissions across the building life cycle will be reduced by over 20%, annual energy use will decrease by more than 25%, tap water consumption will drop by 35%, and resource recovery rates will reach 60%. Recycled materials will be used in construction, and Building Information Modeling (BIM) technology will be adopted to ensure comprehensive environmental benefits throughout the life cycle.\\n\\nLinks: \\nGovernance Achievement Platform - \\'Baogao Smart Industrial Area\\': https://wedid.ntpc.gov.tw/Governance/Detail/G1RBlNd4PJgY",
