        "Please explain": "本府研擬制定本項計畫主要涵蓋5大面向與12個議題，包含氣候變遷因應、治山防災管理、環境影響評估、大氣環境、流域治理、化學物質管理、陸域生態保育、海洋保育、資源循環、環境科技、環境教育及社會參與等，針對面臨之環境調站提出對應策略及機制，並結合局處間行政資源，以維護本縣環境資源及生態平衡，實現安居樂業、低碳城市之願景。 This assessment report mainly consists of 5 major aspects and 12 issues, including climate change response, mountain management and disaster prevention management, environmental impact assessment, atmosphere environment, river basin management, chemical substance management, ecological conservation in land, marine life conservation, resource circulation, environmental science and technology, environmental education and social participation, etc. The County government assesses future risks and provides strategies and mechanisms to face the environmental impacts. Cooperating with various administrative resources, the County government maintains natural resources and ecology systems to build a low-carbon city with happiness."
