        "Please explain": "在面臨氣候變遷的威脅下，因應本縣具有優良的日照條件，因此能源轉型便成為本府推動重點項目之一，而在推動綠能的同時，亦兼顧聯合國永續發展指標(SDGs)。 例如本府推動的「嚴重地層下陷區太陽光電計畫」與「高樹太陽光電示範計畫」，透過將原有不利於農業耕種的土地，轉型活化設置再生能源，讓土地恢復地力、減少地層下陷沉降速率，亦提供農村年長地主土地利用新選項，同時創造在地就業機會，讓專業人才留在屏東，已符合SDG7-可負擔的潔淨能源、SDG8 尊嚴就業與經濟發展、SDG9-產業創新與基礎設施、SDG13-完備減緩調適行動等至少8項指標，有效接軌國際永續發展潮流。 To face impacts of climate change, Pingtung County Government is committed to developing solar energy due to the long insolation hours in Pingtung County. Energy transformation has become one of the key projects in recent years. When promoting green energy, Pingtung County Government also takes citizens' rights into consideration, responding to the SDGs of the United Nations. The solar PV projects in severe subsidence areas and Gaoshu solar PV demonstration project transform non arable land into solar PV plants, which not only provides new options for elderly farmers, but also creates local job opportunities, responding to SDG7 (affordable and clean energy), SDG8 (decent work and economic growth), SDG9 (industry, innovation and infrastructure), and SDG13 (climate action)."
