        "Describe how the factor supports or challenges the adaptive capacity of your jurisdiction": "1. 屏東縣政府在林邊溪上游興建亞洲第一座大型人工地下水庫大潮洲地下水補給湖，從林邊溪上游引水補給地下水，兼具分洪功能。 結果表明，在各種防洪作業下，人工湖可使淹沒深度、淹沒量和淹沒風險降低，淹沒風險降低高達8.18%。2. 大潮洲人工湖的洪水減災和偏遠地區微電網和難民中心的設置，可以使住所免受氣候變化災害的影響。1. Pingtung County Government built the Asia's first large-scale artificial underground reservoir, DaChaoZhou groundwater recharge lake, in the upstream of Linbian River to introduce water from the upstream of Linbian River to recharge the groundwater, which can also provide flood diversion function. The results indicate that under various flood prevention operations, the artificial lake can lead to reduced inundation depth, inundation volume, and inundation risk, and the reduction of inundation risk can be as much as 8.18%.https://ndltd.ncl.edu.tw/cgi-bin/gs32/gsweb.cgi?o=dnclcdr&s=id=%22106NPUS5020001%22.&searchmode=basic2. Mitigation of flooding by DaChaozhou Artificial Lake and the setting of microgrids and refugee centers in the remote areas could shelter the residence from climate change disasters. "
