        "Describe how the factor supports or challenges the adaptive capacity of your jurisdiction": "由於從農村地區遷移到城市，人口老齡化已成為屏東縣面臨的最大挑戰之一。老年人口達到20.21%，導致救災、醫療等公共服務困難。Due to the migration from rural areas to cities, the aging population has become one of the biggest challenges in Pingtung County. The elderly population reached 20.21%, which resulted in the difficulty of public services such as disaster relief and medical treatments."
