    "q3_1_1": [
      {
        "question_text": "Provide information on and an attachment (in spreadsheet format)/ direct link to your main community-wide GHG emissions inventory.",
        "row_order": 1,
        "row_name": "Response",
        "Main community-wide emissions inventory attachment (spreadsheet)^": "112年屏東縣溫室氣體排放清冊-改AR5版本-6(最後版本).xlsx",
        "URL link (with unrestricted access)^": "attached file: 112年屏東縣溫室氣體排放清冊 ",
        "Status of main community-wide inventory attachment and/or direct link": "The emissions inventory has been attached",
        "Year covered by main inventory^": "2023",
        "Boundary of main inventory relative to jurisdiction boundary^": "Same - covers entire jurisdiction and nothing else",
        "Population in year covered by main inventory": 794997.0,
        "Primary protocol/framework used to compile main inventory": "Regional or country/area specific methodology",
        "Tool used to compile main inventory": "Internal tool/process",
        "Gases included in main inventory^": "SF6|N2O|HFCs|CO2|NF3|CH4|PFCs",
        "Primary source of emission factors^^": "Default IPCC emission factors",
        "Source of global warming potential values": "IPCC Fifth Assessment Report (2013)",
        "Has the main inventory been audited/verified?": "Yes, internally audited/verified (self-verification)",
        "Overall level of data quality": "Emissions factors - High data quality|Activity data - High data quality",
        "Have any of the calculation methodologies and/or boundary used for this inventory changed when compared to the previously reported inventory?": "No changes to the methodology and/or boundary used when compared to the previously reported inventory",
        "Additional/historical inventories and other relevant attachments": "111年屏東縣溫室氣體排放清冊-0419v10(全) (4).xlsx",
        "Further documentation, links and comments": "2000年代初，台灣政府傾向於建立溫室氣體盤查方法。但是，由於各市排放類別、計算方法、活動數據的選擇、數據來源等方面的差異，導致其缺乏客觀性。 為此，環境保護署（EPA）提出了《城市級溫室氣體清單指南》，清單遵循政府間氣候變化專門委員會（IPCC）制定的國際地方政府溫室氣體排放分析協議（IEAP）。 《城市級溫室氣體清單指南》不僅遵循了溫室氣體清單的五個基本原則：相關性、完整性、一致性、準確性和透明度，而且與國際趨勢高度接軌。在這種情況下，該方法被認為是每個城市減少溫室氣體的自我評估，並且在國際上是可檢查和可驗證的。就清單氣體而言，HFCs、PFCs 和 NF3 也被列入清單。 然而，台灣政府禁止使用 HFC 和 PFC，因此排放量為零。 NF3為半導體產業排放，屏東縣無相關企業，因此排放量為零。 因此，沒有 HFC、PFC 和 NF3 排放。In the early 2000s, Taiwan's government tended to build a method for GHG inventory. However, the lack of objectivity results from the differences in the emission categories, calculation methods, selection of activity data, and data sources of the municipalities. Therefore, the＂Guidelines for City Level Greenhouse Gas Inventories＂ were proposed by the Environmental Protection Administration (EPA), and the inventory followed the International Local Government Greenhouse Gas Emissions Analysis Protocol (IEAP) by Intergovernmental Panel on Climate Change (IPCC). The＂Guidelines for City Level Greenhouse Gas Inventories＂not only followed the five basic principles of greenhouse gas inventories: relevance, completeness, consistency, accuracy, and transparency are also highly connected to the international trend. In this case, the method is considered a self-assessment of reducing GHG for each city and being inspectable and verifiable internationally. As far as inventoried gas is concerned, HFCs, PFCs, and NF3 are also included in the list. Nevertheless, HFCs and PFCs are prohibited by Taiwan Government. NF3 is emitted by semiconductor industry, and there is no related company in Pingtung County. As a consequence, the HFCs, PFCs, and NF3 emission is zero."
      }
    ],
