        "Target year of goal^": 2025.0,
        "Description of metric / indicator used to track goal and evidence of implementation": "林業局屏東林區辦管理森林資源，在枋山河沿岸選出8695公頃國有林。 根據Forest Stewardship Council™ (FSC™)國際認證標準，屏東林區辦事處成立。 森林生產中心維護天然林生態環境、生物多樣性，響應全球碳減排，2021年獲得FSC認證。到2023年，原民禁伐補償面積達28,000公頃林地，已提前達標。\\nPingtung Forestry and Conservation Agency, the Ministry of Agriculture, District Office of the Forestry Bureau managed forest resources and selected 8,695 hectares of state forests around Fangshan River. According to international certification standards of the Forest Stewardship Council™ (FSC™), Pingtung Forest District Office established. The forest production center maintains ecological environment of natural forests, biodiversity and respond to global carbon reduction, obtaining FSC certification. Moreover, the County Government promote logging ban compensation in indigenous tribes. In 2023, the area of logging ban has reached 28,000 hectares of forest, which has surpassed the goal of 2030.",
