        "Target year of goal^": 2025.0,
        "Description of metric / indicator used to track goal and evidence of implementation": "屏東縣作為農業大縣，採取代工粉碎、清理、生態農場參與等多種處置方式，減少塑料薄膜、廢枝葉等農業廢棄物的焚燒。 屏東縣於2019年率先設立農膜處理區，農戶可將使用過的農膜帶到該區暫存，再由回收公司再利用，製成其他塑膠製品，減少垃圾焚燒及碳排放。至2023年，已建成9個農用廢棄物暫存區、5個農膜暫存區，提供免費清理服務，處理廢棄物3000餘噸。 為了讓更多農業廢棄物再利用，屏東縣將在2025年前增設5個農業廢棄物暫存區，並與回收公司合作，妥善再利用農業廢棄物，減少碳排放。As a major agricultural county, Pingtung County takes various disposal methods, such as OEM crushing, clearance, and participation of ecological farms, to reduce the burning of agricultural wastes, like plastic films, waste branches and leaves. Pingtung County took the lead in setting agricultural plastic film disposal area in 2019. Therefore, farmers can bring used agricultural film to the area for temporary storage, and recycling companies will reuse them to make other plastics products, reducing the waste burning and carbon emissions.Until the end of 2023, 9 agricultural waste temporary storage areas and 5 agricultural film temporary storage areas have been set up to provide free clearance services, disposing more than 3,000 tons of waste. In order to reuse more agricultural waste, Pingtung County will establish 5 more temporary storage areas for agricultural waste by 2025, and cooperate with recycling companies to reuse agricultural waste properly and reduce carbon emissions.",
