        "Target year of goal^": 2050.0,
        "Description of metric / indicator used to track goal and evidence of implementation": "未來所有的新建築都需要符合綠色建築政策。 所有材料都必須是環保的，屋頂必須在計劃中包括太陽能電池板。All the new construction need to fit into green building policy in the future. All materials need to be eco-friendly and the roof must includes solar panel in the plan."
