        "Target year of goal^": 2027.0,
        "Description of metric / indicator used to track goal and evidence of implementation": "幸福巴士串接偏鄉與城市的交通，協助偏鄉居民就醫就學。2025年服務4.8萬人次，預計到2027年服務 11萬人次。The Happiness Bus connects rural areas with urban transportation, helping residents in remote communities access medical care and education. In 2025, it served 48,000 passengers, and the goal is expected to reach 110,000 passengers by2027."
