        "Base year of goal (or year goal was established if no base year)^": 2025.0,
        "Target year of goal^": 2030.0,
        "Description of metric / indicator used to track goal and evidence of implementation": "以禁伐補償，保留原住民區土地，同時維護民的生存權，依法保育山林者可申請禁伐補償每公頃六萬元。預計2030 年前原保地禁伐補償檢測合格面積達 27,500 公頃。\\nThrough logging ban compensation, indigenous lands are preserved while safeguarding residents' right to livelihood. Those who conserve forests in accordance with the law may apply for compensation of NT$60,000 per hectare. By 2030, the area of indigenous conservation land passing inspection under the logging ban compensation program is expected to reach 27,500 hectares."
