        "Base year of goal (or year goal was established if no base year)^": 2025.0,
        "Target year of goal^": 2030.0,
        "Description of metric / indicator used to track goal and evidence of implementation": "屏東縣創全國之先，整合居家醫療、到宅牙醫、居家護理、行動藥師、行動營養師、行動心理師、行動復能及長照居家服務等八大類之居家照護，由醫療(事)或照服人員評估個案狀況，轉介適當之居家照護服務，實踐醫療平權與全人照護目標。Pingtung County took the lead nationwide by integrating eight categories of home-based care services, including home medical care, in-home dental services, home nursing, mobile pharmacists, mobile nutritionists, mobile psychologists, mobile rehabilitation, and long-term care home services. Medical or care professionals assess individual cases and refer them to appropriate home care services to advance the goals of healthcare equity and holistic care.",
