        "Comment": "屏東縣政府為推動永續城鄉，營造綠建築環境，創造健康生活品質，促進綠色產業，並達到節能減碳及減災目標，特制定本自治條例。藉由法制、社會參與、產業、技術、獎勵等面相推廣宣導屏東綠建築計畫，並從自身公部門做起，規定公有建築物3千萬以上皆必須為綠建築。In order to promote green buildings, Pingtung County Government has enacted the self-governing regulation on green buildings to regulate the social participation. The Self-Government Ordinance was started from public sector, public buildings with construction fee over 30 million New Taiwan dollars should be green buildings."
