        "Year of formal approval of plan": 2023.0,
        "End of year plan": 2024.0,
        "Comment": "外來入侵種綠鬣蜥在高屏地區野外族群快速擴張，造成嚴重農損、河堤結構受損及影響生態平衡。屏東縣政府為有效控制野外綠鬣蜥族群數量，推動移除獎勵計畫，以本縣農產品包括紅豆、有機米、黑豆醬油膏等作為獎勵，吸引民眾共同參與本項計畫，並辦理綠鬣蜥移除教育訓練，將維護生物多樣性及生物棲地保護之理念深根基層。Iguana iguana increases rapidly in Pingtung County, which seriously damages agricultural products, river embankment and ecological balance. To effectively control the number of wild Iguana iguanas, Pingtung County Government has promoted the removal and reward project by providing local agricultural products, including red beans, organic rice, black bean soy sauce, to citizens who captured Iguana iguanas. Moreover, the County government also attracts people to participate in this project by conducting education and training on Iguana iguanas capture to maintain biodiversity and protect the environment."
