        "Provide an attachment to the strategy or standards addressing emissions from the jurisdiction's procurement": "琉行杯_離島綜合建設實施方案.pdf",
        "Provide a link, if applicable, and highlight any specific action(s) the jurisdiction is implementing to reduce emissions from its own consumption": "結合小琉球當地飲料店、便利商店、免稅商店、電動機車出租店及民宿等當地商家設置環保杯租借/歸還站。並營運「琉行杯清洗站」及相關物流系統，建立「琉行杯共享行動循環系統平台」，推動小琉球一次用飲料杯及寶特瓶減量，另與當地導覽團體合作，將琉行杯共享行動納入小琉球生態導覽，建立環境友善的低碳永續經營模式，帶動小琉球無塑低碳觀光旅遊，創造經濟成長與生態保護的雙贏局面。Pingtung County government keeps cooperating with local shops, including local beverage shops, convenience stores, duty-free shops, electric two-wheel vehicle rental shops, and hotels in Liuqui, to set up cup-sharing stations. Residents and tourists can rent cups for free and get discount when buying drinks. After using the cups, people can return the cups to the shops which are listed in Liuqui Cup Sharing Action Circulation System Platform and the used cups will be sent to “Cup Cleaning Station.” More and more cups are borrowed in Liuqui island, and it is estimated that 100,000 cups will be borrowed in 2025. Liuqui island is famous for its beautiful beach and sea. By reducing disposable beverage cups and PET bottles, Liuqui island can not only reduce waste to lower greenhouse gas emission, but also protect marine life to make Liuqui a beautiful island forever. "
