        "Action description and web link to further information^^": "<防災型微電網>為加強屏東山區在強降雨及颱風襲擊期間的區域電網抗災能力，根據IPCC AR5模型、人口、應急設施、疏散措施、社區中心基礎設施等，從自然災害潛在地圖中選擇受災多發的原住民部落 在。 經過實地考察和交叉核對，選擇了11個站點安裝防災微電網系統（DPMS），包括5kW光伏、20kWh儲能、能源管理系統和10kW柴油發電機作為備用應急。 DPMS與台電合作，可在災情發生時，為照明、救生設備、通訊設備等提供綠色電力，讓應急救援單位持續72小時。 該DPMS不僅產生綠色電力，而且在一般時期減少碳排放。 所有 DPMS 均於 2022 年 4 月完成，成功實施了 SDG 7、10、11、13 和 17。<Disaster Prevention Microgrid System (DPMS)>To enhance the regional power grid resilience while heavy rainfall and typhoon struck at mountainous districts in Pingtung, disaster-prone indigenous tribes were selected from natural disaster potential maps based on IPCC AR5 models, population, emergency facilities, evacuation measures, community center infrastructure and so on. After field survey and cross-checking, 11 sites were picked to install the Disaster Prevention Microgrid System (DPMS), including a 5kW photovoltaic, 20kWh energy storage, energy management system, and a 10kW diesel generator as a backup emergency. The DPMS, cooperated with Tai-power Company, can generate the green power for lighting, life-saving appliances, and communication apparatus during the period of disaster, allowing emergency relief units to last 72 hours. This DPMS not only generates green power but reduces carbon emissions in general periods. All the DPMSs were completed by April 2022, successfully implementing SDG 7, 10, 11, 13 and 17.Link:https://sa.ylib.com/MagArticle.aspx?id=5356",
