        "Climate hazard(s) that action addresses": "Heavy precipitation|Hurricanes, cyclones, and/or typhoons|Mass movement|Coastal flooding (incl. sea level rise)",
        "Action description and web link to further information^^": "<強化恆春半島醫療> 恆春半島位於台灣最南端，幅員廣大，面積達829平方公里，其中恆春鎮為本半島唯一行政區，距離屏東市約有一百公里。恆春半島居民醫療大都仰賴三家地區醫院，居民分佈又多為老人與小孩，其就醫便利性不佳。對於醫療資源貧乏的恆春半島民眾而言，更突顯緊急醫療的重要性。恆春半島地區醫療後送路途遙遠，倘遇氣候災害如颱風、強降雨等來臨時，後送時間冗長，影響病人就醫權利，因此本府為強化恆春半島急重症照護能力及提升緊急醫療後送品質，結合醫學中心資源協助恆春旅遊醫院(Hengchun Tourism Hospital)、恆春基督教醫院(Hengchun Christian Hospital)、南門醫院(Nanmen Hospital)及枋寮醫院(FANGLIAO General Hospital)提升急救責任醫院等級並補足醫師人力，目前恆旅為急診、急性腦中風、加護病房中度級能力，南門為急診、緊急外傷中度級能力，恆基為急診、高危險妊娠及新生兒醫療中度級能力醫院、枋寮醫院中度級急救責任醫院（不含高危險妊娠及新生兒醫療）避免因南北奔馳求醫，耗費黃金治療時間。 Hengchun Peninsula is located at the southernmost of Taiwan, with a vast area of 829 square kilometers and about 100 kilometers away from Pingtung City. Residents in Hengchun Township rely on 3 district hospitals for medical treatment. Most of the residents in Hengchun Township are elderly people and children and it is inconvenience for them to go to the doctor. Moreover, lacking emergency medical service is a more serious problem. It takes a long time to get medical evacuation in the Hengchun. The medical evacuation time will be longer during nature disasters, such as typhoon, heavy rainfall, which affects patients' health rights. Consequently, Pingtung County Government combines medical center resources to assist Hengchun Tourism Hospital, Hengchun Christian Hospital, and Nanmen Hospital to improve the level of hospitals and provide sufficient manpower. Hengchun Tourism Hospital is responsible for emergency medical service, Ischaemic stroke, and intensive care unit with moderate level capability. Nanmen Hospital is responsible for emergency medical service and major trauma. Hengchun Christian Hospital is responsible for emergency medical service, high-risk pregnancy and newborn. Fangliao General Hospital is responsible for intensive care unit with moderate level capability (excluding high-risk pregnancy and newborn). By enhancing abilities of medical treatments, patients can save their time and get medical services within golden hours. Link:https://video.udn.com/news/1171008",
