        "Action description and web link to further information^^": "屏東縣農保自2016年起，因氣候變遷於2018年推出天氣參數作物保險。 保險範圍涵蓋蓮霧、木瓜、糖蘋果、甜柿、番石榴、梨、荔枝、大棗、水產等，寒潮、暴雨、洪水、颱風等災害均在保險範圍內。 只要降雨量、風速等氣候條件達到一定標準，農民就可以盡快獲得理賠，節省定損時間。 目前，農業保險尚處於試點階段； 將來可以進行修改和改進。Pingtung County Agricultural Insurance has started in 2016 and launched the weather parametric crop insurance in 2018 due to climate change. The insurance covers wax apple, papaya, sugar apple, sweet persimmon, guava, pear, litchi, jujube, aquaculture, etc. Disasters such as cold waves, rainstorms, floods, and typhoons are covered in the insurance. As long as the climatic conditions such as rainfall and wind speed reach a certain standard, farmers can get claims as soon as possible and save time for determining damage. At present, agricultural insurance is still in the trial period; modifications and improvements could be made in the future. Link:https://www.afa.gov.tw/cht/index.php?code=list&ids=277",
