        "Action description and web link to further information^^": "<恆春半島銀合歡移除及復育造林計畫>恆春半島因銀合歡入侵，對於當地植群生態造成影響，為恢復原有林相，本處積極推動銀合歡移除復育造林，並配合「國土生態保育綠色網絡建置」計畫，以友善環境生態造林方式，導入生態廊道、友善環境、栽植原生樹種等元素，以國有林地為軸帶，從點、線、面串連復育造林，期間並協調各國、公有地經管機關投入防治，相互合作，期能恢復恆春半島原有植群景觀。\\n<Leucaena Removal and afforestation Project in Hengchun Peninsula>On the Hengchun Peninsula, the invasion of Leucaena leucocephala has disrupted the local vegetation and ecosystem. To restore the original forest landscape, the Forestry Bureau has been actively promoting the removal of Leucaena and reforestation efforts. These actions are aligned with the “National Green Network for Ecological Conservation” initiative, adopting eco-friendly afforestation approaches that incorporate ecological corridors, environmentally friendly practices, and the planting of native tree species. Using national forest land as the main axis, reforestation is carried out in a connected pattern across points, lines, and areas. During this process, coordination has also been made with various national and public land management agencies to jointly participate in control measures. Through such collaboration, the goal is to restore the Hengchun Peninsula's original vegetation and natural landscape.\\n\\nLink:https://www.coa.gov.tw/redirect_files.php?id=61392&file_name=Vn28qhS6upGuqcMt255OB8JRrAiEr4ftkpb6mNM5vgT0JfCklsuNsQY3G1WGPlusQcWGSlashwe2AWGEqualWGEqualgyHu4Bl0YEjLCqjGApvscAXYRvhTKyp65aWGSlashDxkTJ2728XIqts9I8jXDeqqHDeZfiRPPTlWu3mUHMxI0h950J",
