        "Action description and web link to further information^^": "由於屏東縣幅員遼闊，且資源分散，往往造成同仁疲於奔命、不易於管理，爰本計畫建構統一指揮調度之智慧運輸中心來整合各類資訊，該中心並非過往交通部門之交控中心，除整合交通、公共運輸資訊外，亦結合縣內觀光景點與活動場域之管理與大數據分析（例如導入AI影像辨識技術，即時掌握景區、停車場之人車流，搭配CMS、APP資訊發布，宣導分流來疏解人車潮），並輔以災害事件資訊(例如:介接雨量、水位警戒及土石流警戒資訊)，以符合屏東縣特有的環境現況、滿足交通旅遊業務之推展需求。 Due to the vast territory and the scattered resources, Pingtung County Government built a smart transportation center to integrate various information. This is not a traffic control center. It integrates traffic and public transportation information, and combines the management and big data analysis of tourist spots and big public events in the county (such as realizing the number of tourists and vehicles in tourist spots and parking lots by AI identification technology, sharing rerouting information and alternative choices by CMS and APP) Smart transportation center also provides disaster information (precipitation, water level warning and landslide warning information) to meet the unique local conditions of Pingtung County and meet the needs of the promoting transportation and tourism.",
