        "Action description and web link to further information^^": "<提升離島緊急醫療能力> 因氣候變遷使小琉球地區形成孤島機率增加，為保全居民生計，商請東港安泰醫院協助，由各專科醫師輪流支援門診診療服務，滿足當地醫療照護需求，當災害發生孤島現象產生時，當地醫療間仍可啟動視訊連線與高雄長庚紀念醫院進行遠距聯絡。另因氣候威脅，常讓本島與小琉球交通中斷，故本府購置可抗7級風浪的慈航輪救護船，將琉球鄉打造為全台唯一擁有救護船鄉鎮；另外配合衛生福利部執行「山地偏鄉離島地區C型肝炎抗體快篩」，提升離島居民醫療檢查便利及多元性。 Due to climate change, Liuqiu Township becomes isolated island easily. In order to protect residents' livelihood, Donggang Antai Hospital is invited to assist residents living in Liuqui Township. Doctors from various specialists will take turns to support medical services to meet local needs. During the disasters, remote medical services can be used and local residents can communicate with Kaohsiung Chang Gung Memorial Hospital. In addition, transportation of Liuqiu Township is often interrupted due to bad weather. Therefore, Pingtung County Government purchased ambulance ferry named Chihang, which can withstand level 7 storms and waves. Liuqiu Township is also the only town in Taiwan with ambulance ferry. Furthermore, Pingtung County Government cooperates with the Ministry of Health and Welfare to implement \\'Hepatitis C Antibody Rapid Screening in Mountainous, Remote and Outlying Islands\\' to improve the convenience and diversity of medical examinations for residents living in outlying islands.",
