        "Action description and web link to further information^^": "為預防傳染病，衛生局建立了多維度的傳染病預防網絡，包括結核病、艾滋病、性病、登革熱、呼吸道感染、胃腸道感染等。 推動並提出了針對不同社區的各種傳染病的衛生和健康教育、對弱勢人群的額外關愛以及傳染病預防策略等實施方案。由於氣候變化，登革熱的防控受到媒介蚊子增加的影響最大。 因此，政府採取了加強檢查和處罰的措施。 政府聯合33個鄉鎮成立全縣登革熱防治消毒小組，對環境進行消毒，包括交通站點、商業場所、人群熱點、學校、公園等。To preventing contagious diseases, a multi-dimension prevention network for infectious diseases, such as tuberculosis, HIV/AIDS, sexually transmitted diseases, dengue fever, respiratory tract infection, and gastrointestinal tract infection, was set by Public Health Bureau. Several implementations, such as sanitation and health education for various infectious diseases among different communities, extra caring for vulnerable populations, and strategies of contagious disease prevention, have been promoted and proposed.Due to climate change, the prevention and control of dengue fever are the most important affected by the increase in vector mosquitoes. Therefore, the government adopts enhanced inspections and penalties. The government cooperated with 33 towns established the county's dengue fever prevention and disinfection team to disinfect the environment, including transport stations, commercial places, crowds hot spots, schools, parks, etc to protect the homeland.Link:https://www.ptshb.gov.tw/Default.aspx",
