        "Action description and web link to further information^^": "<宜居部落建設計畫與安全防減災機能補助計畫>因應氣候變遷下，極端降雨事件的發生頻率與強度皆有增加的趨勢，也造成面臨各種災害的風險，包括崩塌、土石流及淹水等，亦有大幅提升的現象。因此，未來部落所研擬之永續發展策略，應再納入極端氣候的影響，朝向更具有韌性的調適策略進行整體性的營造。屏東縣政府於災害徵兆調查及部落訪談(地方服務團、縣府公所共同前往部落進行)推動「宜居部落建設計畫-安全防減災機能補助計畫」，進行部落調查時，一併辦理有關部落災害風險、防減災調適需求之風險溝通與意見交流，施作防災設施類型包含基礎民生維生設施、基礎防(減)災設施、多功能防災設施，預計規劃完成12部落盤查及藍圖規畫並與族人溝通等，以完善本縣災害預警能力。< Livable tribe construction and adaptative project >Extreme rainfall and various climate disasters are increasing due to climate change. As a result, sustainable development strategies for the indigenous tribes should consider the impact of extreme climates and build more resilient adaptation strategies.The Pingtung County Government promotes the \\'Livable Tribal Construction and Mitigation Project” to hear indigenous people's opinions about adaptation strategies when visiting tribes. Disaster prevention facilities include life supporting facilities, basic adaptation facilities, multi-function disaster prevention facilities. The county government are going to complete tribe surveys and blueprints of disaster prevention to enhance resilience in indigenous tribes.Link:https://www.cip.gov.tw/zh-tw/news/data-list/9A8362871EA0BBFF/91111270B6DD95255C40979E2DEBE40D-info.html",
