        "Action description and web link to further information^^": "<海水供水系統>臺灣沿海地區地勢較低，又因土壤鹽化無法耕作，加上近年來海洋漁業資源日漸枯竭，沿海居民遂築堤養殖，又其大面積魚塭集中地區發生地層壓密沉陷現象等，使得外界質疑養殖業者超抽地下水做為養殖使用及私設管路越堤抽取海水水之舉，常成為環境、海(河)堤構造物破壞之潛在因素。故藉由海水供水系統統籌計劃，不僅提供養殖漁民純淨及穩定海水，並促使養殖漁業在此地區穩定發展及達到防災、減災保護養殖產業安全之目標。<seawater supply system>Coastal areas are relatively low and cannot be cultivated due to soil salinization. Coastal residents built embankments for aquaculture, which is considered as a reason of land subsidence. overexploitation of groundwater by aquaculture damages the environment. Therefore, an overall planning of seawater supply system can not only provide pure and stable seawater for aquaculture, but also promote the stable development of aquaculture in coastal areas and achieve the goal of disaster prevention and mitigation to protect coastal safety.Link:https://udn.com/news/story/7327/7137043",
