        "Action description and web link to further information^^": "<小琉球聚落式污水處理設施>屏東縣政府為改善琉球鄉的海域水質，已陸續完成三座聚落式污水處理設施，第四座聚落式污水處理設施於112年10月啟用，全島四座聚落式污水處理設施約可處理全島90%生活污水，有機物及懸浮固體物去除率高達90%以上，有效解決琉球鄉生活污水處理問題，同時可維護周邊海域水質及海洋生態，讓本縣之光-綠蠵龜有個乾淨優質的家。\\n\\n< Settlement sewage treatment facilities in Liuqui island > In order to improve water quality near Liuqui island, Pingtung County Government has set up 3 settlement sewage treatment facilities and operation of the fourth one was started in October, 2023. The four sewage treatment facilities can treat 90% of wastewater and solve the problem of water pollution to protect marine life, including our Chelonia mydas. \\n\\nLink:https://www.pthg.gov.tw/plantou/News_Content.aspx?n=B666B8BE5F183769&s=000300DDDE2E5450\\n",
