        "Climate hazard(s) that action addresses": "Heavy precipitation",
        "Action description and web link to further information^^": "<水質永續管理>東港溪為屏東縣主要河川之一；為解決匯入東港溪排水長期受到民生污水及畜牧廢水影響、提升生活及生態環境品質，於東港溪上游設置龍頸溪排水漫地流水質淨化設施、民治溪溼地淨化設施、甘棠水質淨化場，及內埔龍頸溪水質淨化場(全國首創魚菜共生水質淨化場) 等，另於高屏溪流域設置殺蛇溪水質淨化場、萬年濕地群(含黃金濕地、圳寮濕地及海豐濕地)，改善河川水質。\\n< Sustainable management of water quality >Donggang River is one of the major rivers in Pingtung County. To address the long-standing impact of domestic sewage and livestock wastewater discharged into the river, and to enhance both living and ecological environmental quality, multiple water purification facilities have been established along its upper reaches. These include the Longjing Creek floodplain water purification facility, the Minzhi Creek constructed wetland, the Gantang Water Purification Plant, and the Neipu Longjing Creek Water Purification Plant—the nation's first aquaponics-based water purification facility. In addition, in the Gaoping River basin, the Shashe Creek Water Purification Plant and the Wannian Wetland Complex (including the Huangjin, Zhenliao, and Haifeng wetlands) have been developed to further improve river water quality.\\n\\nLink 1: https://www.pthg.gov.tw/News_Content.aspx?n=EC690F93E81FF22D&sms=90586F8A7E5F4397&s=D218BF10D0B41811Link 2:https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/3365847",
