        "Action description and web link to further information^^": "<行動藥師>本府考量強降雨造成道路中斷、影響出門取藥意願，為服務領有慢性病處方箋之年邁獨居或子女同住但無法代其領藥等有需求縣民，藉由長期照護處、社會處、衛生所或民間機構轉介有需求個案，透過社區藥局藥師執行送藥到宅，與提供藥物諮詢服務，解決病患領藥不便、用藥錯誤的問題，達到藥物整合及降低就醫次數的目的。< In-home care services >Pingtung County Government provides care services by sending pharmacists to patients' home to provide medicines and pharmacy counseling to solve the problems, such as traffic disruption caused by heavy rainfall, elderly or disabled people who live alone, people who live in remote areas. In order to provide services for the residents in need, the Department of Longterm Care, Department of Social Affairs, Public Health center and NGOs are responsible to collect those cases and pharmacists in community will provide In-home services to those patients to reduce health risks and protect their health rights.Link:https://www.pthg.gov.tw/plantou/News_Content.aspx?n=B666B8BE5F183769&s=65685242D1A1BDAD",
