        "Action description and web link to further information^^": "<自主防災社區>自民國99年起，水利署針對易淹水地區輔導縣市政府開始推動水患自主防災社區，透過防汛組織、教育訓練、演習演練、社區互訪及宣導等活動，提升社區成員防救災觀念，使民眾面對水患時，能有自救、互救的能力，減輕水患對人民生活之衝擊。而現今屏東縣已有37處水患自主防災社區。< Autonomous flood Prevention Community >Since 2010, the Water Resources Agency has guided the county and city governments to promote autonomous flood prevention communities in areas with high risks potential. Through activities such as flood prevention education and training, regular drills, community visits, and public information campaigns to enhance residents' awareness of disaster prevention and make residents have abilities to save themselves and each other. Pingtung County has 37 autonomous flood prevention communities now.Link:https://wrafpc.tw/web/community/2022/06/02/%E5%B1%8F%E6%9D%B1%E7%B8%A3%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C/",
