        "Action description and web link to further information^^": "<逐步提升私人載具電動(氣)化比例>補助汰換燃油機車、限制販售非生質燃料及禁用燃油汽機車，以低碳運具停車優先或保障空間作為誘因，逐步將汽機車進行電動(氣)化，預計將於2030年、2040年及2050年前分別完成89,471台(30%)、193,855台(65%)及298,239台(100%)電動汽車汰換量，及185,688台(30%)、1402,324台(65%)及618,960台(100%)電動機車汰換量。<Gradually increasing the proportion of private electric vehicles>Pingtung County Government subsidizes electric vehicles, and restricts the sale of fossil fuel vehicles to replace fossil fuel vehicles with electric ones. It is estimated that there will be 89,471 (30%) electric cars replaced by 2030, 193,855 (65%) electric cars replaced by 2040, and 298,239 (100%) electric cars replaced by 2050.There will be 185,688 (30%) electric motorcycles replaced by 2030, 1,402,324 (65%) electric motorcycles replaced by 2040, and 6,18,960 (100%) electric motorcycles replaced by 2050Link:https://www.ptepb.gov.tw/News_Content.aspx?n=6ADAD0C8CF25613A&sms=B1FB4F08559B3920&s=2996CC128033DE7F",
