        "Primary emissions sector addressed and action type^": "Waste: Install municipal recycling points or centres (for residents or businesses)",
        "Action description and web link to further information^^": "<建置農業廢棄物多元化處理最佳化體系>\\n農業廢棄物妥善處理率長期作物達93%，短期作物更高達98%，創歷年新高。環保局於今年度將再持續精進各項管制措施，以達成民眾對於空氣品質再提升的期望。\\n當進入農作物剪枝旺季，環保局持續推動多元妥善處理方式協助農友解決農業廢棄物處理困境，包含代工破碎、免費代清運與集中場暫置等作法。\\n目前木質農業廢棄物集中暫置場設置於九如、內埔、南州、東港、潮州、佳冬、林邊、枋寮及高樹共9處；農膜集中暫置場設置於九如、內埔、潮州、東港、枋寮共5處，並可提供農民申請免費代清運服務，農民若有農業廢棄物妥善處理問題或申請代清運服務，可撥打環保局專線將有專人解答，請農友們務必配合勿露天燃燒，共同維護環境及空氣品質。若發現有露天燃燒情形將依空氣污染防制法逕行加重告發處分，處行為人新臺幣1200元以上10萬元以下罰鍰，請農友們務必配合善加利用各項輔導補助方案，以共同維護本縣空氣品質。\\n<An optimal system for treatments diversity of agricultural waste>\\nThe proper disposal rate of agricultural waste has reached 93% for long-term crops, and 98% for short-term crops. Pingtung County Government will keep improving various control measures to meet the citizens' expectations of better air quality.\\nPingtung County Government promotes multiple and proper treatments in the peak season for crop pruning to handle agricultural waste, including crushing, cleaning, and transport services for free, and storing at designated sites. \\n\\n Woody agricultural waste is temporarily stored in 9 central storage sites in Jiuru, Neipu, Nanzhou, Donggang, Chaozhou, Jiadong, Linbian, Fangliao and Gaoshu Township. Agricultural film is temporarily stored in 5 places in Jiuru, Neipu, Chaozhou, Donggang and Fangliao Township. \\n\\nFarmers can apply for free cleaning and transport services. If farmers have problems with the proper disposal of agricultural waste or apply for cleaning and transportation services, they can call the special line of the Environmental Protection Bureau and staffs will answer the questions. Open burning is banned by “Air Pollution Control Act”, people who will break the law will be fined.\\n\\nLink: https://www.cna.com.tw/postwrite/chi/308257\\nLink: https://www.cna.com.tw/postwrite/chi/308257",
