        "Action description and web link to further information^^": "<電動車友善充電環境 >「淘汰二行程機車換購電動二輪車補助計畫」、「新購電動二輪車補助計畫」推動民眾汰換或新購電動二輪車，提升低污染二輪運具使用率。113年本縣運具電動化成果斐然。電動汽車數量展現強勁成長，從112年底的815輛，大幅增長45.4%，於113年底達到1,185輛。電動機車亦穩健增加，年底達 21,351 輛，其總數持續穩居非六都縣市第二名的佳績。<Friendly Environment for electric vehicles>The Pingtung County Government has combined the \\'subsidy program for replacing motorcycles with two-stroke engine with electric two-wheel vehicle\\' and the \\'subsidy program for newly purchased electric two-wheel vehicle\\' to promote new electric two-wheel vehicles, and to increase the usage rate of low-pollution two-wheel vehicles. In 2024, Pingtung County achieved remarkable results in vehicle electrification. The number of electric cars showed robust growth, rising from 815 at the end of 2023 to 1,185 at the end of 2024—an increase of 45.4%. Electric motorcycles also grew steadily, reaching 21,351 by year-end, maintaining the County's strong record of ranking second among non-six-metropolitan-area counties and cities.\\n\\n Link:https://reurl.cc/WGyzV7",
