        "Action description and web link to further information^^": "公共自行車五倍增站增量計畫\\n2022年11月引進YouBike 2.0，已於2023年2月正式啟用，截至114年5月，已建置154站、1,905輛公共自行車（含電輔車），113年使用人次達172.1萬。未來將持續檢討站點效益，提升服務覆蓋率。\\n\\n<Public bicycle rental services: rental stations will be five times more>\\nYouBike 2.0 was introduced in November 2022 and officially launched in February 2023. As of May 2025, a total of 154 stations and 1,905 public bicycles (including e-bikes) have been established. In 2024, usage reached 1.721 million trips. Moving forward, the County will continue to review station effectiveness and further enhance service coverage.\\n\\nLink:https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aloc/202211150228.aspx",
