        "Select a reference ID for the action": "Mitigation Action 6",
        "Primary emissions sector addressed and action type^": "Generation of grid-supplied energy: Low or zero carbon energy supply generation",
        "Action description and web link to further information^^": "2009年因莫拉克颱風而完成的「Aqua Solar Farm」項目（裝機容量23.4MW）後，我們正朝著100%綠色電力的方向邁進，以滿足屏東的家庭用電需求。屏東於2016年成立首個「綠色能源推廣辦公室」，推廣綠色能源。屏東在參與ICLEI舉辦的「100%可再生城市與區域網絡」後，旨在通過綠色能源實現國內電力100%的目標。“嚴重地層下陷區（SSA）”和“複合式土地利用”戰略。\\n根據美國能源部發布的GIS工具指南，我們從SSA的13,000公頃非耕地中選擇了大約3,800公頃用於安裝太陽能(PV) 發電廠。在不影響公共設施功能的情況下，實現了多功能用地，包括蓄水池漂浮太陽能裝置和堤防、垃圾填埋場、學校庭院地面太陽能板等綠色能源。我們為利益相關者提供平台，同時調整費用監管以吸引投資者，因為SSA項目可以成為全球其他城市學習的三贏模式。2025年8月屏東縣再生能源總設置量已達到1,497.70MW。預計至2040年底，裝機容量可提升至3GW。\\n\\nAfter the completion of the \\'Aqua Solar Farm\\' project (installed capacity 23.4MW) due to typhoon Morakot in 2009, Pingtung County keeps moving towards 100% green electricity to meet the household electricity demand. Pingtung County Government established the first \\'Green Energy Promotion Office\\' in 2016 to promote green energy.\\nAs a participant of the \\'100% Renewables Cities and Regions Network\\' held by ICLEI, Pingtung County puts efforts on achieving the goal of providing 100% renewable energy for citizens by projects named “Severe Subsidence Area (SSA)” and \\'Multi-function Land Use”.\\nTo implement the SSA project, 3800 hectares of potential sites were selected from 13,000 hectares in severe land subsidence area by GIS software. According to the data of Taipower Company, there is the potential to have 1GW grid connection in this area.\\nFurthermore, the project of multi-functional land use is to install solar PV panels without affecting the functions of public facilities, including floating PV devices on a retention pond and ground-mounted PV panels on the dike, landfill, and court at school for green energy. We provide a platform for stakeholders while adjusting regulation on the fee to attract PV investors for the SSA project could be a triple-win model for other cities to learn around the world. Installed capacity of renewable energy in Pingtung County has reached 1,497.70MW, and it is estimated that the installed capacity will reach 3 GW by the end of 2040.\\nLink:https://pge.pthg.gov.tw/",
        "Start year of action": 2018.0,
