        "Action description and web link to further information^^": "<高污染鍋爐汰換>\\n以熱泵鍋爐或電熱設備替代高汙染鍋爐，加強高污染鍋爐進行管制及汰換，至2023年已完成128座鍋爐汰換。此外，亦輔導鍋爐進行污染防治設備改善，累計至2023年已完成207座鍋爐改善作業，透過稽查輔導作業，推動68家工廠污染減量，2023年轄內70座燃材鍋爐於全數完成防制設備裝設。\\n\\n<Replacement of high-pollution boilers>\\nPingtung County Government keeps replacing high-pollution boilers with heat pump boilers or electric heating equipment and has completed the replacement of 128 high-pollution boilers until 2023. Moreover, the County Government also assisted in preventing boiler pollution. 207 boilers have been improved until 2023. The County Government assisted factory in reducing pollution through inspections and counselling. 70 firewood burning boilers have installed pollution prevention equipment in 2023.\\n\\nLink:http://ptaq.green99.com.tw/index.php/inquire2",
