        "Description of collaboration and any progress, if applicable": "1.\\tJointly promoted by government departments, the public, and operators to establish solar photovoltaic systems in various regions of the city.\\n2.\\tTo Promote the Green Roof Public Participation Plan, Government departments cooperate with the public and operators. The public will provide roofs for operators selected by the City to install solar photovoltaic, and promote the installation of solar photovoltaic in various areas of the City. At present, the areas have covered all administrative regions of the City, and have included the industrial zone under the Industrial Development Bureau of the Ministry of Economic Affairs, the science and technology industrial park under the Administrative Office of the Processing and Export Zone of the Ministry of Economic Affairs and the Science Park under the Ministry of Science and Technology, so as to increase the installation capacity of solar photovoltaic in the City.\\n3.\\tFor the self operated parks of the city government, more green space and various types of trees will be planned, and for private parks and adjacent industrial expansion cases, manufacturers will also be required to plant more trees to increase the offset of carbon emissions.\\n",
