        "Description of collaboration and any progress, if applicable": "To reduce exhaust emissions from old diesel buses, Taichung City encourages bus operators to replace old buses with new ones, giving priority to electric buses. By the end of July 2025, 293 electric buses were on the road, distributed on 38 bus routes operated by 9 bus operators, accelerating the city's move towards electrified buses. It is expected that all buses will be electrified by 2030.",
