        "Description of collaboration and any progress, if applicable": "Through the Taichung City Urban Design Review System, promote urban building greening and effectively improve the urban living environment; Designs such as green roofs, vertical greenery, and plant walls can reduce urban heat island effects and protect ecological diversity; In addition, the review system also ensures residents' needs and expectations for the natural environment, enhancing public awareness of environmental protection and sustainable development.",
