        "Areas collaboration focused on": "Other: Taichung City's Initiative to Implement Sustainable Development Goals",
        "Description of collaboration and any progress, if applicable": "The Mayor of Taichung City and Ambassador Chien Yu-hsin, Chairman of the Taiwan Sustainable Energy Foundation and Advisor to the National Climate Change Strategy Committee of the Presidential Office, signed the Taichung City \\'Public Sector Sustainable Development Initiative,\\' pledging that Taichung City will continue to strengthen institutional governance, expand social influence, and promote environmental sustainability.",
