        "Comment": "Initiate the local government's proactive investigation system for diseases and pests - conduct monitoring and investigation in accordance with the \\'16 Specific Disease and Pest Monitoring Plans\\', \\'Autumn Armyworm Monitoring Plan\\', and \\'Pear Rust Disease Monitoring Plan\\' - the selection of monitoring areas, investigation period, investigation items and methods, and monitoring results reporting, and report the monitoring results to the \\'Plant Epidemic Notification System\\'（ https://phis.aphia.gov.tw/masterpage-1 ）The long-term investigation area is provided as a reference for integrated prevention and quarantine decision-making.\\nRegarding the plan to promote the proactive investigation system of local government diseases and pests, the Agriculture Bureau of Taichung City Government has recognized that specific diseases and pests have caused serious agricultural losses in the past, but from occurrence to expansion, there is no comprehensive monitoring mechanism to provide early warning for areas that have not yet occurred to immediately initiate prevention and control work. We hope that through the implementation of this case, we can grasp the latest situation of diseases and pests in the production area, and through appropriate warning systems, immediately report and initiate relevant epidemic prevention work before they spread, minimize disasters, reduce agricultural losses, and carry out investigations on birds, plants, fish, shrimp, crabs, and water quality for the ecological conservation and management of Gaomei wetlands. This can serve as a reference for reviewing and revising conservation plans.\\n"
