        "Comment": "Due to the dramatic climate change caused by global warming, the intensity and frequency of natural disasters are increasing, leading to increasing risks in agricultural production. In line with the Ministry of Agriculture's agricultural insurance policy, we are promoting agricultural insurance. Through insurance mechanisms and premium incentives and subsidies, we aim to reduce farmers' losses from natural disasters, maintain stable incomes, and diversify their risks. Furthermore, we are strengthening the promotion of agricultural insurance policies, continuously expanding agricultural insurance products, and increasing insurance coverage to achieve the goal of protecting farmers' incomes."
