        "Target type^": "Renewable energy generation target: Increase generation of renewable energy (all energy types)",
        "Target description": "1.\\tOur city actively develops renewable energy, among which in terms of solar photovoltaic, to reduce the impact on the environment, we mainly use rooftop solar photovoltaic installed on existing buildings as the main driving force. We actively implement policies such as the establishment of photovoltaic systems in the municipal management office, the participation of the entire population in green energy roof projects, the fulfillment of obligations by large households, specific factory guidance, and photovoltaic subsidies. Our goal is to achieve 1GW of solar photovoltaic power by 2030.\\n2.\\tThe city actively promotes offshore wind development and cooperates with the Ministry of Economic Affairs' phase III of block development operations. In phase I, the Taichung Fengmiao project site, invested by the Copenhagen Infrastructure Partners, has been selected and obtained a total development capacity of 500MW. It is expected to operate in parallel in 2027, with a target of achieving a 1GW offshore wind power installation capacity by 2030. \\n",
