        "Provide a link, if applicable, and highlight any specific action the jurisdiction is implementing to reduce emissions from the consumption of goods and services in this category": "1.\\tIn addition to repairing second-hand furniture, the city's Baozhilin waste furniture recycling center also has second-hand clothing, bags, shoes, and other items for exhibition and sale\\n2.\\tBy promoting a green procurement system between government agencies and private organizations, relevant businesses can participate in the production of environmentally friendly products or provide environmental services, forming a green consumption cycle between the manufacturing and procurement ends of environmentally friendly products, and implementing a \\'green consumption\\' model that is environmentally friendly.\\n"
