        "Action description and web link to further information^^": "Sunshade - Melody Plan 3.0: In response to extreme weather conditions and hot summers, in order to prevent adults and children from getting sunburned or Heat stress while engaging in leisure activities in the park, and to ensure that they can play in the park at any time, Mayor Lu has upgraded the Melody Plan to 3.0 version. In addition to maintaining friendliness, the project will also add shading facilities in conjunction with the unique environment of the game field, creating a high-quality leisure space 24 hours a day.\\nhttps://www.construction.taichung.gov.tw/2537239/post",
