        "Proportion of the total jurisdiction population within the jurisdiction boundary (specified in 1.2) with increased resilience due to adaptation action (%)": "81-90%",
        "Proportion of natural or modified terrestrial, freshwater, coastal and/or marine ecosystems within the jurisdiction boundary (specified in 1.2) with increased resilience due to adaptation action (%)": "81-90%",
        "Funding source(s)": "Public-private partnerships|Jurisdiction's own resources",
