        "Describe if and how climate-related scenarios have informed the plan": "Taipei City 2050 Net Zero Emissions Action White Paper 2.0, in addition to incorporating the Paris Agreement's target of limiting warming to 1.5°C, the IEA's \\'Net Zero by 2050: A Roadmap for the Global Energy Sector\\' released in 2021, referenced the IPCC's Sixth Assessment Report on Climate Change (AR6) Volumes 1 to 3 (WG 1~3) to develop other related projections and scenarios in order to formulate localized carbon reduction adaptation strategies and climate actions.",
        "Primary author(s) of plan^": "Dedicated team within jurisdiction|Relevant department within jurisdiction",
        "Assessment of co-benefits, trade-offs, and synergies of actions included in plan": "Plan assesses synergies of actions",
