        "Describe if and how climate-related scenarios have informed the plan": "Taipei City's Greenhouse Gas Control Implementation Plan (Phase 2) will be implemented from 2021 to 2025. In addition to incorporating the Paris Agreement's target of limiting warming to 1.5°C, the IEA's \\'Net Zero by 2050: A Roadmap for the Global Energy Sector\\' released in 2021 and the IPCC's Sixth Assessment Report on Climate Change (AR6) Volumes 1 to 3 (WG 1~3) are used to develop other related projections and scenarios in order to formulate localized carbon reduction strategies and climate actions.",
