        "Area of plan, policy and/or strategy": "Climate emergency declaration",
        "Name of plan and URL link, if applicable": "Promote the installation of photovoltaic power systems on public premises\\n1.https://www.doed.gov.taipei/News_Content.aspx?n=7A008DCFBE16BA98&sms=1E9E50982373D28A&s=75CCC1B88031CA92\\n2.https://tpcems.tier.org.tw/open/renewable-energy ",
